---
title: Caribbean Honey Pork with Corn-Cauliflower Rice & Mayo
description: Enjoy a flavour-packed, guilt-free and nutritious meal with our cauliflower rice! With colourful veggies stirred in and topped with our classic Caribbean-spiced pork loin steak, we know you'll be glad you took the plunge and gave this low carb delight a go.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

